Name of Post:

SSC Upcoming Exam Calendar 2022-23 for CHSL, MTS, CGL, JE, JHT, Driver, SA, Etc Exam
Post Date / Update: 06 July 2022 | 12:38 PM
Short Information : Staff Selection Commission (SSC) has released the tentative Revised calendar of various exams CGL, CHSL, Junior Hindi Translator, Scientific Assistant, Driver, CPO SI, Delhi Police, Constable GD, Junior Engineer, Etc to be held in 2022 - 2023. This information has also been given in the revised calendar of SSC, when the advertisement of which exam will be released, what will be the last date of application and when will the exam be held. All the candidates who are preparing for SSC exam must see this revised calendar.
) }
